Class JsonReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.comfortanalytics.aon.AbstractReader
      • com.comfortanalytics.aon.json.JsonReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aconstants, Areader, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class JsonReader
extends AbstractReader
implements java.io.Closeable
    Json implementation of Areader. The same instance can be re-used with the setInput methods. This class is not thread safe.
